snippet.title: Fashion Dreamer - Release Date Announce - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Fashion Dreamer is coming to Nintendo Switch on November 3, 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/fashion-dreamer-switch/

Share your unique sense of style with the world in a brand-new fashion influencer experience! Enter a virtual world of fashion fantasies made real, where coordination and communication mix like never before. Your new life as an influencer awaits!

#FashionDreamer #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/

Like Nintendo on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/Nintendo
